1.title: Episode #1.1

episode of.title: Honda Insight LA2NOLA: Adventures in Efficiency (TV Series 2009– )

1.plot: Jamal, Leebo, Zoe and Mike are first introduced to the Honda Insight and are given the official rules for their upcoming "Adventures in Efficiency: LA2NOLA" road trip challenge.

2.title: Episode #1.2

episode of.title: Honda Insight LA2NOLA: Adventures in Efficiency (TV Series 2009– )

2.plot: Zoe and Mike make their way to Joshua Tree and stop to admire the gorgeous surroundings. Mike is slightly distracted by his new discovery of "tweeting". Jamal and Leebo find themselves lost near the border of Arizona.

3.title: Episode #1.3

episode of.title: Honda Insight LA2NOLA: Adventures in Efficiency (TV Series 2009– )

3.plot: Zoe and Mike have a minor disagreement on their drive to Yuma and Zoe decides it's time to teach Mike a lesson. Mike finds himself in for a surprise when he notices his photo on a "WANTED" sign at the Territorial Prison National Park.

4.title: Episode #1.4

episode of.title: Honda Insight LA2NOLA: Adventures in Efficiency (TV Series 2009– )

4.plot: Jamal and Leebo visit the Saihati Camel Farm, where Leebo discovers he's the king of road trip bingo, while Zoe and Mike spend some time relaxing in New Mexico at the Riverbend Hot Springs.

5.title: Episode #1.5

episode of.title: Honda Insight LA2NOLA: Adventures in Efficiency (TV Series 2009– )

5.plot: Both teams meet up unexpectedly at the International UFO Museum in Roswell, where Jamal is trying to convince Leebo that aliens do exist. The teams make a pact to reconnect again in New Orleans at the end of the trip.

6.title: Episode #1.6

episode of.title: Honda Insight LA2NOLA: Adventures in Efficiency (TV Series 2009– )

6.plot: Leebo challenges Jamal to finish a 72oz. steak in under an hour at The Hoffbrau in Austin, while Mike believes that he can romantically impress Zoe under the city's famous bat bridge.

7.title: Episode #1.7

episode of.title: Honda Insight LA2NOLA: Adventures in Efficiency (TV Series 2009– )

7.plot: In this final episode, both teams meet up at a local restaurant to share stories about the adventures they've encountered along their drive from Los Angeles to New Orleans - and more importantly, who won.

imdb.plot outline: Four people from Los Angeles - two long-time friends and a newlywed couple - have been given the opportunity to take an all-expense paid trip from LA to New Orleans. The only caveat - it's a road trip. And they have been challenged to get there most efficiently using the features inside the new Honda Insight. What will they encounter along their journey?
